definitions: Discover or perceive by chance or unexpectedly.
Discover oneself to be in a particular situation.
Summon up (a quality, especially courage) with an effort.
(of hunters or hounds) discover game, especially a fox.
Discover or experience to be the case.
Ascertain by study, calculation, or inquiry.
Discover the fundamental truths about one's own character and identity.
Experience or regard (something) in a specified way.
(of a court) officially declare to be the case.
Reach or arrive at by a natural or normal process.
Reach one's destination, typically without first knowing how to get there.
Reach the understanding or conscience of.
